law.text:
As used in this chapter:
"Secretary" means the secretary of the Cabinet for Health and Family Services.
"Cabinet" means the Cabinet for Health and Family Services.
law.history: Amended 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 99, sec. 524, effective June 20, 2005. -- Amended 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 426, sec. 468, effective July 15, 1998. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 74, Art. VI, secs. 107(1), (11), and (22). -- Created 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 370, sec. 4.
